4495.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4495.description: SpongeBob and Patrick get caught in the feud between a crew of ghost pirates and the Flying Dutchman.

4496.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
4496.description: As the kids are pursued relentlessly by a mysterious machine, their exhaustion puts them at each other's throats.

4497.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
4497.description: When Aang struggles with a block while trying to learn Earthbending from Toph, he wonders if the problem is with him or his teacher. Meanwhile, Sokka gets himself in a jam.

4498.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4498.description: When SpongeBob suddenly becomes the richest citizen of Bikini Bottom, he finds himself surrounded by lots of new "friends" who are more than happy to help him spend his money. // It's the day of Squidward's big lead solo audition with the Bikini Bottom Men's Chorus, and Squidward is brimming with excitement. He's positive he's a shoo-in for the part.

4499.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4499.description: Mr. Krabs hatches up yet another get-rich-quick scheme: professional wrestling! But Mr. Krabs isn't the one who's going to wrestle. // The new Mermaid Man and Barnacle Boy trading cards are on sale, and SpongeBob is determined to get the super special rare talking card, no matter how many packs of cards he needs to buy to find it.

4500.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
4500.description: An upset Mikey runs away from home and befriends a Mutant Frog in the woods. When he learns its Frog family plans to attack the human world, he has to figure out a way to stop them.

4501.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
4501.description: Creatures that feed off dreams trap the Turtles inside their own dreams as April and Casey must find a way to wake them up.

4502.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4502.description: After the Croc Bandits steal Shifu's favorite ruby-encrusted statue of Oogway from Po and Tigress, the two warriors must team up to get the statue back and return it home.

4503.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4503.description: When Po learns a kung fu move that can erase someone's short-term memory, he takes it too far.

4504.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4504.description: It's off to the races when Skipper agrees to give a day off from hard training to the first penguin who can bring him a kipper. Private, Rico, and Kowalski battle their way to a fish packing plant where they discover Officer X has become Fishmonger X. The deranged X sniffs out the fighting penguins, capturing them and hauling them off to the pokey. Can they rediscover the teamwork they had forsaken in order to escape? High Moltage: The penguins are determined to make opening day of their favorite action star's blockbuster movie! Private, however, has an itchy problem - he's turned hideous because he's molting! The penguins need his hypercute powers to knock Alice out and disengage her new zoo security system. The despondent bird does all he can to reconstruct his cuteness, but sadly his hypercute powers distort to cause a hyperalarming, hypervomitous mess!

4505.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4505.description: The Penguins are faced with a global battle when their specialty food-making machine belches out a toxic cloud that threatens not just the zoo, not just the city, but the earth itself!

4506.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4506.description: The Chimpanzee beneficiaries of Sandy's undersea treedome are paying a visit to see what progress she has made with her inventions. But Sandy doesn't think any of her work will satisfy the chimps. // The Flying Dutchman takes up residence at SpongeBob's house where he proceeds to scare, startle and surprise SpongeBob around the clock.

4507.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4507.description: Mr. Krabs wants to give his daughter Pearl the best birthday ever. While he works on the party, SpongeBob is assigned the task of figuring out what Pearl would like for a present. // SpongeBob receives an invitation to take part in a competition on mysterious Karate Island for the chance to be crowned "King of Karate".

4508.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4508.description: During an intense day on the job, SpongeBob's spatula breaks mid patty-flip. With his favorite kitchen implement out of commission, SpongeBob searches for a temporary replacement. // When a wishing well is installed near the Krusty Krab, Mr. Krabs sends SpongeBob down in a bucket to collect the coins that will be dropped by people making their wishes.

4509.title: Nella The Princess Knight
4509.description: When the Tooth Fairy doesn't show up for a Fleagle, Nella investigates her mysterious disappearance. // With his arm in a cast, Garrett must find a new way to be a hero on an urgent knightly quest.

4510.title: Nella The Princess Knight
4510.description: Nella and Trinket's perfect tea party goes wrong when they accidentally use boingy-berries in their muffins. // When Nella and Riley are asked to rock-sit, they don't realize the importance of their mission.

4511.title: Bubble Guppies
4511.description: The Bubble Guppies are going on a camping trip! Grab your flashlights and gather around the campfire to make s'mores and hear about the spooky legend of Pinkfoot!

4512.title: Bubble Guppies
4512.description: Gil wants to adopt a puppy! But before he can bring the puppy home, the Bubble Guppies must learn how to take care of pets.

4513.title: Dora the Explorer
4513.description: When young Pablo loses his magic flute, a terrible drought hits his family's farm. Dora and Boots find Pablo's flute, and hurry off to return it to Pablo on his Mountain.

4514.title: Dora the Explorer
4514.description: Dora and Boots keep running into friends in need of help. Turns out the other animals are all headed to a big party at the Treehouse. They beg Dora and Boots to come too!

4515.title: Rusty Rivets
4515.description: When Crush wanders off and gets lost, Rusty invents a night flyer to find him in the dark. // When Liam loses his stuffy out the train window, Rusty goes on a retrieval mission using a mechanical spider suit to climb up under the trestle and drop down like a spider to get it.

4516.title: Rusty Rivets
4516.description: When a rare bird builds his nest in a dangerous location and can't be persuaded to move, Rusty and the gang rebuild his habitat. // Rusty and Ruby build a cupcake flinging machine that goes out of control.

4517.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
4517.description: When Blaze and Starla encounter a herd of cows wandering out in the desert, they must embark on a wild west adventure to bring them back to Starla’s barn.

4518.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
4518.description: It's the day of the Dragon Island Duel, a race around tropical Dragon Island! But when Crusher cheats and sends Blaze away before the race, AJ must set out to rescue his best friend and bring him back to the starting line.

4519.title: PAW Patrol
4519.description: Ryder and the PAW Patrol need to rescue Alex on Jakes mountain. // The pups find strange footprints in the snow on the mountain outside Adventure Bay. Everyone thinks it's a "snow monster" and it's scaring the skiers away.

4520.title: PAW Patrol
4520.description: Ryder gets a call from the Circus ringmaster – Ellie the baby elephant has escaped from the circus train! // Mayor Goodway’s purse chicken “Chickaletta” has gone missing. Ryder and the Paw Patrol search Adventure bay.

4521.title: PAW Patrol
4521.description: Ryder and the PAW Patrol have to rescue Alex when he takes off on his new “super trike”. // Marshall proves he is a true hero when he stops to put out a real fire on the beach during a race against the clock for a trophy.

4522.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4522.description: Sandy Squirrel comes down with a case of the blues and SpongeBob is determined to find out why and what he can do about it. // The evil Plankton is up to no good once again when he tries to manipulate SpongeBob into becoming aggressive and mean in order to get more out of life.

4523.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4523.description: Its April Fools Day, one of SpongeBob's favorite days of the year because he gets to play harmless pranks all day long (even if most people don't get them). // On a visit to the Fry Cook Hall of Fame, SpongeBob inadvertently pulls a mythical spatula from a vat of ancient grease, thus giving him claim to the title of "Worlds Greatest Fry Cook".

4524.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4524.description: Pat gets a new pair of shoes, but doesn't know how to tie his laces. When SpongeBob offers to demonstrate lace tying to Pat , he forgets how to do it. // Mr. Krabs takes the day off from the Krusty Krab and puts Squid in charge for the day. Squid seizes the opportunity to take the day off as well and he leaves SpongeBob alone to man the store.

4525.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4525.description: Private hones in on his cuteness factor and BOOSH! Any witness or potential threat is instantly disabled - adorability has been weaponized. // In the haste of a zoo animal meeting, King Julien and Skipper are agreed to switch places for a single day.

4526.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4526.description: Private's quirky Uncle Nigel pops in for a quick visit from across the pond. // The boys intercept a fax with cartographic news; Maurice has only 24 hours to live. In order to make Maurice's assumed final day comfortable, the entire zoo bands together.

4527.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4527.description: As the annual Winter Festival approaches, Po doesn't have enough money to buy his dad the present he deserves, so he takes a job as a bounty hunter to capture a dangerous escaped convict for the reward. But Po's plan doesn't go as smooth as he hoped.

4528.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4528.description: Po takes on the challenge of training a lovable but klutzy member of the Emperor's family. However, will Po's training be enough to protect them both from the evil designs of a traitor in their midst?

4529.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
4529.description: A new mutant called Muckman starts to gain notoriety as NYC's "Monster Hero".

4530.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
4530.description: The Shredder kidnaps and experiments on the Mighty Mutanimals.

4531.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4531.description: SpongeBob will do anything to get to meet his newest hero, Kenny The Cat. // Attempting to get more work out of Squidward, Mr. Krabs spins the story of the monstrous Yeti Crab, which eats lazy workers.

4532.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4532.description: In order to save money, Mr. Krabs fires SpongeBob. Unable to just “do nothing”, SpongeBob decides to go back to work doing anything, anywhere.

4533.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4533.description: SpongeBob tries to take a shortcut to work, but becomes lost along the way. // After failing his driver’s test again, Mr. Krabs decides to teach SpongeBob how to drive himself.

4534.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4534.description: When a rhino comes to the Valley of Peace seeking to destroy the Dragon Warrior, Po tries to befriend him before he discovers Po's true identity.

4535.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4535.description: After Po unleashes an 'impossible move', he's told that the most powerful fighter in the Valley of Peace always turns evil, and that's him!

4536.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4536.description: King Julien is literally bounced out of his kingdom and onto the New York streets. A kindly old lady thinks he's a cat and swoops him up. He's encroaching on another's turf, though - the apartment's already home to a feline-impersonator, a female ferret named Zoe. Julien is taken with Zoe, and puts on his best seduction moves. Will the street-smart ferret succumb to his kingly charms? Smart money says... you never know! Action Reaction: Skipper is forced to live his worst nightmare when he's doused with Inflatium and stress causes him to blow up like a balloon. Guess what this means... no more going on missions! Sitting behind a desk doing paperwork instead! Hans takes advantage of the situation and targets a massive weapons lab, and without Skipper the penguins are easily captured. How can Skipper combat the evil puffin if he's in a puffy state?

4537.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4537.description: Kowalski has a rival, if you even can call it a rivalry. A Delaware Blue Hen has taken up residence at the zoo, and she has the amazing ability to predict the future! Kowalski doesn't buy the psychic chicken hype and sets out to discredit her. The truth turns out to be far more sinister than a simple sports-pickin' chicken, and Kowalski will have to use all his best moves to wiggle out of this mess. Thumb Drive: The penguins need a thumb, and Maurice's fits the bill nicely. Using the opposable digit thumbprint to break into a secret weapons lab gets the penguins all atwitter. King Julien is unhappy that his right hand man is running around on missions with the birds so he sets out to sabotage the mission. As with most of King Julien's plans, this scheme turns out to be "thumbs down"!

4538.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
4538.description: Casey and Donnie bond over building Casey's new hot rod, but their newfound friendship is challenged by Speed Demon, a hot-rodding mutant who is terrorizing the roads.

4539.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
4539.description: When Casey, Raph, Mikey and Donnie are captured by a new mutant, both April and Leo must overcome disabilities in order to save them.

4540.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4540.description: Mermaidman and Barnacleboy let SpongeBob and Patrick in on their secret, heroic origins! // Using SpongeBob's DNA, Plantkon grows himself a second eye...and becomes nice!

4541.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4541.description: The night before the big school dance, Mr. Krabs asks SpongeBob to help Pearl get rid of a barnacle on her face. // SpongeBob asks Patrick to pet-sit Gary while he's away at his Grandma's birthday party.

4542.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4542.description: House Sittin’ for Sandy: SpongeBob house-sits for Sandy, and all is quiet until Patrick shows up. Smooth Jazz at Bikini Bottom: After losing their passes, SpongeBob and Squidward try to sneak backstage at the sold-out Kelpy G show.

4543.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4543.description: After Po disobeys Shifu's orders, the Hierarchy of the Sacred Onyx Council replaces Shifu with a new master who banishes the Furious Five and plans to destroy Shifu.

4544.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4544.description: When Mantis returns to his hometown claiming to be the Dragon Warrior to impress his ex-fiancé, Po pretends to be his sidekick who doesn't know kung fu.

4545.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4545.description: Private's in heaven - icy, freezing heaven. The Lunacorns on Ice extravaganza is in town, and Skipper's determined to take him as a treat. Accompanied by unexpected fellow fanboys Bing and Roy, the gang heads to the arena. Things get a bit d-icey when the gorilla and rhino end up on the ice with the lunacorns. The enraged director is ready to shutter the whole thing unless they find some way to slip 'n slide out of it. Showdown on Fairway 18:A legendary putter is at the center of controversy when the Amarillo Kid returns to the zoo. The slippery armadillo needs Private's help to make good on an ill-advised bet with two gopher brothers. Who's the bad guy here though? The gophers show up at the zoo to actually warn the penguins about the kid! The story takes us on more twists and turns than a Pebble Beach golf hole!

4546.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4546.description: King Julien's archrival, Clemson, returns in another attempt to claim the lemur crown. This time the sneaky lemur has a document that "proves" King Julien is not the legitimate king because he wasn't born in Madagascar. A series of challenges to prove who's more kingly ensues, and the penguins try to stack the deck in Julien's favor by each switching brains with him. Simple, right? How could a plan like this possibly fail? Private and the Winky Factory: Private's favorite treat, the Peanut Butter Winky, is going the way of the dinosaur. Distraught that the snack cake is ceasing production, Private urges a raid on the Winky Factory where the last remaining Winkies are rolling off the production line. Impressed by Private's passion, Skipper gives him command of the mission! The young penguin learns there's a heck of a lot to digest when leading a team.

4547.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
4547.description: A professor leads the kids to a spirit library in the middle of the desert, where Sokka hopes to discover powerful secrets to use against the Fire Nation.

4548.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
4548.description: Aang searches for Appa, while Katara struggles to keep everyone together so they can survive in the vast desert. Meanwhile, Uncle and Zuko seek help from an ancient secret society.

4549.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4549.description: The Krabby Patty That Ate Bikini Bottom: Mr Krabs uses Sandy’s experimental growth formula on a Krabby Patty with disastrous results. Bubble Buddy Returns: SpongeBob tries to keep Bubble Buddy’s visiting son, Shiny, out of trouble and away from sharp edges.

4550.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4550.description: Restraining SpongeBob (fka Whispering Tentacles): Annoyed by SpongeBob for the last time, Squidward issues him a restraining order. Fiasco! (fka The Priceless Patty): Plankton steals a Krabby Patty from the Krusty Krab, unaware it’s really an art piece by famous artist Fiasco.

4551.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4551.description: Mr. Krabs manufactures Krabby Patties on an industrial scale, but it drives a wedge between SpongeBob and Patrick.

4552.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
4552.description: Leo takes the Turtles to train in the woods in an advanced ninja ritual where they must overcome their weaknesses and face their greatest enemies in order to become true ninjas.

4553.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
4553.description: The Turtles return to the city to search for Splinter, only to find that the city is overrun with Kraang.

4554.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4554.description: Shifu tells the citizens of the Valley of Peace that whoever can defeat Po before sunset will become the new Dragon Warrior. When Hundun hears of the challenge, he returns to the village to claim the title.

4555.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4555.description: After Po gets trapped in a hole, Fung helps him out and is owed a favor. Will it be a costly one?

4556.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4556.description: Kowalski invents an enemy detector. As is often the case, it doesn't work, and Skipper gets his own wires crossed when he smashes it. Old enemies are now friends and old friends are now enemies as the boss bird starts to systematically clean out the zoo with the help of his new friend Hans. King Julien gets into the act by becoming Skipper's friend too, going so far as to Congaga dance together. New BFF Hans is not happy with the new bromance, however. Could this be the opening the penguins need? // The annual Zoo Snooze is here! Kids get to buy tickets for a zoo sleepover, a treat the animals look forward to every year! This year's going to be very different, however, when the rotten Vesuvius Twins buy up all the tickets themselves. The zoosters plan to turn the tables, though, and exact sweet revenge on the twins. The penguins, influenced by Private of course, can't let this happen, and it's a long night's journey into day as the penguins scramble to protect their one-time tormentors.

4557.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4557.description: HALF- HOUR SPECIAL (Conan O’Brien is voicing the villain Kuchikukan): The Penguins are faced with a World Domination battle when Private accidentally unleashes KuchiKukhan the Destroyer of Worlds. Can they stop him in time to save the World?

4558.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4558.description: Fred the Squirrel has hit the jackpot. He stumbles onto a jackpot oak tree which is loaded with acorns (that's tons of money to animal folk). He's going to need financial advice, and who better to offer sound advice than King Julien? The two enter a partnership looking for ways to spend on the good life. The Red Squirrel has designs on the loot, though, and captures the hapless twosome in order to squeeze the acorns out of them. Will the evil squirrel's precisely planned plot pay or get him played? The Terror of Madagascar: A special delivery has come from Madagascar. What is it? A baby Fossa! Everyone is enchanted by the little tyke except King Julien, who sees him as a lemur-devouring predator, and he has the toothmarks on his butt to prove it! Julien formulates a plan to get rid of the adorable little carnivore, but his slithery solution becomes much worse than the problem!

4559.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4559.description: After Plankton drives away Mr. Krabs' customers, Mr. Krabs is forced to give out free Krabby Patties to try to win them back. // SpongeBob's pineapple is falling apart, and he needs all of his friends to help him remodel it!

10942.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
10942.description: Karen 2.0 (fka Computer Trouble): Plankton’s computer wife Karen ends up working at the Krusty Krab after being replaced by the newer, better Karen 2. InSPONGEiac: SpongeBob can’t get to sleep, and asks for help from Patrick—who thinks he can’t stay awake.
